# Entebbe Airport Slotting System — Implementation Plan

Build a Python Django web application for managing airline seasonal flight scheduling and airport resource allocation at Entebbe International Airport (EBB). The system handles flight requests from airlines, allocates stands/gates/check-in counters, and detects scheduling conflicts.

