### API Routes

#### [NEW] [core/views.py and core/urls.py]
- Dashboard with stats, season info, quick actions
- `GET /flights` — List all flight requests with season filter
- `GET /flights/new` — New flight request form
- `GET /flights/<id>/edit` — Edit flight request form
- `POST /flights` — Create flight request
- `POST /flights/<id>/edit` — Update flight request
- `POST /flights/<id>/delete` — Delete flight request
- `GET /schedule` — Daily schedule view with date picker
- `POST /schedule/allocate` — Auto-allocate resources for a date
- `GET /resources` — Resources overview (stands, gates, counters)

